Cc: Guenter Roeck <groeck@chromium.org>
Cc: stable@vger.kernel.org
Signed-off-by: Dominique Martinet <dominique.martinet@cea.fr>
Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>
---
